commit.message: Fix test suite when TMPDIR has no trailing slash
Fix potential use of null pointer in test plugin
Fix C++ test build on MacOS
Avoid overriding state features passed by the host

Fix potential null dereferences and conversion warnings

A few of these can't actually happen, but that's opaque to static analysis, so
appease clang-tidy with casts since the checks are too valuable to suppress.
Fix null dereference when trying to load state from a missing file
Fix crash when plugins pass NULL to the LV2_State_Retrieve_Function

Explicitly specify all documentation dependencies

Yet another attempt to sort out flaky documentation builds.  This tries to be
careful and describe the complete documentation dependency graph to meson
explicitly (ignoring tool outputs that aren't used).

Format meson.build files with muon

The less time wasted with manual code formatting, the better.
Clarify threading rules for instance functions
Update sord dependency version to match siblings
Fix manifest URIs for bundle URIs without trailing slashes
Fix static default LV2_PATH value on MacOS
Clean up documentation and remove junk files from install
